r of the Order of the Aztec Eagle is awarded to Her Majesty Queen Margrethe II of Denmark|url=http://dof.gob.mx/nota_detalle.php?codigo=5029819&fecha=13/02/2008|date=13 February 2008|publisher=Secretariat of the Interior|accessdate=11 December 2014}}</ref>\n* {{flag|Morocco}}: Grand Cordon of the [[Order of Ouissam Alaouite]]<ref name=\"QueenMargretheOrdersPage\" />\n* {{flag|Netherlands}}: Knight Grand Cross of the [[Order of the Netherlands Lion]]<ref name=\"QueenMargretheOrdersPage\" /><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.pinterest.com/pin/464081936578471504/|title=Staatsbezoek Denemarken 2015 twee koninginnen. - Koninklijke Familie/Royal Family/ Famille Royal - Pinterest - Denmark, Dutch and US states|work=Pinterest|accessdate=7 April 2016}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Dutch State Visit to Denmark|url=http://members.boardhost.com/BeneluxRoyalJewels/msg/1415689637.html|publisher=Benelux Royal Jewels| date=11 November 2014|accessdate=26 August 2015}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Dutch State visit to Denmark - Gala Dinner at Christiansborg Palace| url=http://www.newmyroyals.com/2015/03/dutch-state-visit-to-denmark-gala.html?m=1|publisher=New My Royals|date=17 March 2015}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.anp-archief.nl/attachment/47226 |title=Photographic image |website=Anp-archief.nl |accessdate=16 March 2017 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150923172353/http://www.anp-archief.nl/attachment/47226 |archivedate=23 September 2015 |df=dmy-all }}</ref>\n* {{flagicon|Kingdom of Nepal}} [[Shah dynasty|Nepalese Royal Family]]: Member of the [[Mahendra Chain]]<ref name=\"QueenMargretheOrdersPage\" />\n* {{flagicon|Kingdom of Nepal}} [[Shah dynasty|Nepalese Royal Family]]: Member Grand Cross of the [[Nepal Pratap Bhaskara|Order of Honour]]<ref name=\"QueenMargretheOrdersPage\" />\n* {{flag|Norway}}: Grand Cross with Collar of the [[Order of St. Olav]]<ref name=\"QueenMargretheOrdersPage\" /><ref>{{cite web|url=https://s-media-cache-ak0.pinimg.com/564x/